{"tid":510101,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺d連登仔笑鳩d人去台灣讀書好撚可憐","createTime":"2017-12-26T06:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T06:45:02.000Z","uid":68626,"like":5,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4a100548e2a687a8ff9597e475103c3909b3735a","tid":510101,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:29:19.000Z","msg":"九成九都係窮撚黎<br />\n無錢出國留係香港讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地就去台灣見識下<br />\n開擴眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班local撚一係酸一係窮<br />\n仲可以食台妹 同埋學好普通話<br />\nd憤青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaf1826f32483a85ccf43bf89f65ab007b8c60c","tid":510101,"uid":21000,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"台灣都開擴到眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f683fefb44b813eefd0bf34820f0aff97a48ec4","tid":510101,"uid":71728,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"去台灣都唔有錢得去邊<br />\n利申：DSE 1 take 入ugc grad冇defer<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dd1dcf98b55f3af320025eaf12fa1b47c2d911","tid":510101,"uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":103,"score":-101,"quote":{"pid":"ebaf1826f32483a85ccf43bf89f65ab007b8c60c","tid":510101,"uid":21000,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"台灣都開擴到眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"台灣有乜問題？係人都知香港無論邊間大學，教學風氣、學生質素、師資等全部輸蝕畀台灣好多間大學，做人放眼世界，崇優鄙劣，唔想起香港讀書浪費時間同青春有乜問題？<br />\n連登就係咁多廢人同小朋友，以為起呢個所謂DSE考到高分就叫精英，人地台灣一早推行大學普及化，唔適合預科制度既人都可以升上去大學，而呢D大學（尤其台灣）教學極為嚴謹，點都會TRAIN到你變成個有能力既學生。睇到連登同香港人就知緊係要去台灣接受高等教育，同你班井底之蛙讀書真心浪費時間青春。"},{"pid":"947644915114db06c2057952a2c2ac9448e2cc48","tid":510101,"uid":54181,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已