你變成個有能力既學生。睇到連登同香港人就知緊係要去台灣接受高等教育，同你班井底之蛙讀書真心浪費時間青春。</blockquote>大學普及化係美帝諗出黎既戇鳩野，真正意思係賺錢，美帝學費貴，私立幾皮野美金一年，公立唔少都要一兩皮美年一年，造就左好多sugar daddy科水食女同埋好多永世唔還loan既本土畢業生<br />\n<br />\n人地歐洲佬有良心，賺錢都係賺外人錢，自己友學費低/免費<br />\n<br />\n更加唔駛講美帝為左大學普及化而發明出黎既通識教育，簡直係cap水招數既極致，歐洲佬又係有良心冇跟<br />\n<br />\n至於你話咩台灣d大學好過香港，science engine 可能係既，其他就真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><strong>science engine 可能係既</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你曲定直呀<br />\n</strong></span>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"人地奧數奧物奧化金牌數量屌打香港 台大各engine同science major大撚把保送入去<br />\n<br />\n差D唔記得香港連奧化都冇玩<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩&quot;人地人口多,金牌自然多&quot;<br />\n<br />\n新加坡奧物都拎左40塊金牌<br />\n<br />\n我係憎台灣 但唔會好似你咁盲反"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:31:00.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係盲反 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且我唔唔清楚 台大各engine是否屌打香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你不如試下去台灣讀番個civil / EE degree 之後返HK 睇下揾唔揾到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n或拎住台大engine degree去問下 HKIE  人地個charter engineer exam 睇下人地會否 show off 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>List of Accredited Programmes</strong>  我就見唔到有台大份<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkie.org.hk/en/quali/progaccredlist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkie.org.hk%2Fen%2Fquali%2Fprogaccredlist%2F&d=WopXK2SOPlMnIw00Z1swJARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9328b585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkie.org.hk/en/quali/progaccredlist/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T21:21:31.000Z","msg":"小弟理性咁講小小個人意見<br />\n理論上去咗台大EE讀，基本都唔太打算翻香港，以唔係過美國進修，一唔係係當地工作攻埋個碩士<br />\n<br />\n畢竟NTUEE出嚟人工係台灣好高，雖然啱啱畢業嘅話同香港平均月入差唔多，不過台灣消費平香港太多，而且升上去人工都起碼2-3萬港紙（唔包花紅）<br />\n<br />\n而且NTUEE我覺得一件幾唔錯嘅嘢就係真係好多大公司同跨國企業台灣分部專門去EE度R人實習，例子就唔講啦，呢個sem我見到有唔少，真係資源好多<br />\n<br />\n唔似香港人搵工翻，NTUEE出嚟係工搵你做<br />\n<br />\n臺大電機呢四個字&hellip;&hellip;其實真係工程領域入面幾乎無人不曉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw雖然我讀緊，但係專業能力係另一領域，所以畢業之後都係打算翻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261a0dcab845aa75c391cad8eab1ddc37ac43db2","tid":510101,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e268c16ced3ceff5a1f305f78c3dc21a4a31acb","tid":510101,"uid":77052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e7bbd34a5884a6506aa50eb80cd5b0192bb77f","tid":510101,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dab85987ec14bc3dd370ed5276a3fdc032f94b4b","tid":510101,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"人地奧數奧物奧化金牌數量屌打香港 台大各engine同science major大撚把保送入去<br />\n<br />\n差D唔記得香港連奧化都冇玩<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩&quot;人地人口多,金牌自然多&quot;<br />\n<br />\n新加坡奧物都拎左40塊金牌<br />\n<br />\n我係憎台灣 但唔會好似你咁盲反"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:31:00.000Z","msg":"首先我唔係盲反 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且我唔唔清楚 台大各engine是否屌打香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你不如試下去台灣讀番個civil / EE degree 之後返HK 睇下揾唔揾到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n或拎住台大engine degree去問下 HKIE  人地個charter engineer exam 睇下人地會否 show off 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>List of Accredited Programmes</strong>  我就見唔到有台大份<br />\n<a href=\"ht